'''2011年缅甸地震'''（{{lang-my|၂၀၁၁ မြန်မာငလျင်}}）是当地时间2011年3月24日晚发生在[[缅甸|缅甸]]东北部[[掸邦|掸邦]]境内一次[[地震|地震]]。[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]]给出的初步结果是震级6.8级<ref name=USGS>{{Cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usc0002aes.php |title=Magnitude 6.8 – MYANMAR |accessdate=2011-03-30 |archive-date=2011-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110630101620/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usc0002aes.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，震源深度10公里；[[中国地震台网中心|中国地震台网中心]]给出的震级为7.2级，震源深度20公里；緬甸軍政府則認爲是7.0級。震中距离中国[[云南省|云南省]]边境地区大约80公里。中国云南、[[广西|广西]]等地均有明显震感。<ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-hans | publisher = 凤凰网 | title = 7.2级地震考验“金三角” | url = http://finance.ifeng.com/roll/20110325/3752994.shtml | date = 2011-03-25 | accessdate = 2011-03-25 | archive-date = 2018-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180118010539/http://finance.ifeng.com/roll/20110325/3752994.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = Zh-hans | publisher = 新华网 | title = 云南广西等地紧急应对缅甸地震影响 | url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/society/2011-03/25/c_121230371.htm | date = 2011-03-25 | accessdate = 2011-03-25 | archive-date = 2011-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110514084705/http://news.xinhuanet.com/society/2011-03/25/c_121230371.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

